@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_hzqttb(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (v1 * (wp.cos(v1 + 0.01) * (tmp + 0.84 * v2 + 0.17)))
    v1 = v1
    tmp = (wp.cos(v2) / 0.31)
    v1 = wp.abs(0.29)
    tmp = wp.sin(0.03)
    v0 = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.25) + (v1 + 0.61 + v1 + 0.28)) / (0.21 - (v0 + 0.44 + tmp + 0.37)))
    data[tid] = v0
